[sudo] password for psh: === [04-master-join] 시작: k8s-master3 ===
--- [1/3] join 명령어 확인

아래 내용을 k8s-master1 에서 확인하세요:
  cat scripts/k8s-install/join-tokens/kubeadm-init-full.log | grep -A 10 'control-plane'

형식 예시:
  kubeadm join 10.10.120.229:6443 \
    --token <token> \
    --discovery-token-ca-cert-hash sha256:<hash> \
    --control-plane \
    --certificate-key <cert-key>

